Some prereqs : 
sudo apt-get install git
sudo apt-get install docker.io


Install Istio:

https://istio.io/docs/setup/kubernetes/quick-start/


After Istio install : 
Installing and example application (will use istio afterwards) : 

https://codefresh.io/docs/docs/deploy-to-kubernetes/codefresh-kubernetes-integration-demochat-example/

will want the demo app at : https://github.com/containers101/democh

git clone https://github.com/containers101/demochat
